ENDSUBENT           22
SUBENT        14864003   20260226   20260508   20260508       1528
BIB                  6          8
REACTION   (8-O-17(N,P)7-N-17,,SIG,,FIS)
DETECTOR   (LONGC) The detector for the fast neutrons from N17
           was a fast neutron "long counter" with its sensitive
           face eight inches from the tank.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No details on sources of uncertainties.
CORRECTION Corrected for a background of 0.6 cpm.
